      "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You reduce your primary target to 0 Hit Points using @UUID[Compendium.starfinder-field-test-for-pf2e.actions.Item.6ctkxUnVwqooSvgg]{Auto-Fire}.</p><hr /><p>With a subtle gesture of your weapon and a stare, you remind a survivor of your onslaught that there's more where that came from. @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.2u915NdUyQan6uKF]{Demoralize} a single creature that was in the area of your Auto-Fire with a +2 circumstance bonus. If you have legendary proficiency in Intimidation or if you have the @UUID[Compendium.starfinder-field-test-for-pf2e.class-features.Item.0gR2k1paeKXs5OsS]{action hero} fighting style and the target of Collateral Witness is the enemy closest to you, you can use this as a free action with the same trigger.</p>"
